The spiritual journey takes a digital leap with the launch of the Bhagva App – now LIVE! This new-age platform for bhakti and devotion was inaugurated in the presence of Delhi’s respected Chief Minister, Shrimati Rekha Gupat ji, along with Ex-MP Shrimati Sunita Duggal ji. The event was further sanctified by the presence of Sudhanshu ji Maharaj, esteemed sadhus, and revered mahamandaleshwars. The grand launch celebration was beautifully enriched by soulful performances from legendary singer Kailash Kher ji, MP Shri Manoj Tiwari ji, and the talented Renuka ji, making it a spiritually uplifting experience.

With the Bhagva App, you can now access daily pujas, live darshan, horoscopes, bhajans, and much more—anytime and anywhere. It brings devotion to your fingertips, helping you stay connected to your faith in this fast-paced world. Download the app today and embrace bhakti in its modern, digital form. Stay blessed, stay connected.
